from shapely.geometry import Point, shape

endcol = []
startcol = []

for i in trips.index:
    endDistrict = "Out of Town"   
    point = Point(trips['endLon'][i], trips['endLat'][i])
    for feature in js['features']:
        polygon = shape(feature['geometry'])
        if polygon.contains(point):
            endDistrict = json.dumps(feature['properties']['name'])
            break
    endcol.append(endDistrict)
        
for j in trips.index:
    startDistrict = "Out of Town"
    point = Point(trips['startLon'][j], trips['startLat'][j])
    for feature in js['features']:
        polygon = shape(feature['geometry'])
        if polygon.contains(point):
            startDistrict = json.dumps(feature['properties']['name'])
            break
    startcol.append(startDistrict)
        
trips['endLoc'] = endcol
trips['startLoc'] = startcol
